tasks/folder-picker-ux/codex-phase8-rerun.raw.log:393:tasks/folder-picker-ux/criteria-execution-log.md:16:| 6 | a11y WCAG AA 4.5:1 + Tab order | ✅ (contrast + tab order + Phase 7.5 v2 회복 + Phase 7.5.6 font bump 재검증) ⏳ (Lighthouse + owner SR smoke 잔여) | Phase 3 self-audit + **localhost computed 재확인** (`preflight-localhost-verification.md`): `--fg2 rgb(82,82,82)` on `--bg rgb(255,255,255)` = **7.52:1** (helper/row/hint 모두 동일) / kbd `--fg rgb(10,10,10)` on `--surface-muted rgb(250,250,250)` = **20.4:1** / `--young-coconut-dark` outline-only(text 미사용). Tab 순서 10 tabbables: close 첫 → 2 pickers → 5 timeframe → 폼 필드 = 자연 순서. **Phase 7.5 v2 contrast 회복** (`phase7.5-auxiliary-verification.md`): Edit 2 v2 `.kbd-label` 색상을 `--fg3 #8E8E8E` (3.28:1 AA fail) → `--fg2 #525252` (codex v2 권장 반영)으로 변경 → **production 재계산 PASS**: kbd `18.97:1` / label `7.81:1` / hint `7.81:1` / code (inherit `--fg2`) `7.81:1`. **a11y 추가 강화** (Edit 3 v2 신규 클래스 `.path-preview-hint code` JetBrains Mono / Edit 4 inline `<kbd aria-label>` 2건 + `<span aria-hidden>` 1건): SR이 `⌘⇧.`을 "Command Shift Period"로, `Ctrl+H`를 "Control H"로 또박또박 발음 + `(period)` 시각 라벨은 SR 중복 announce 차단. **Phase 7.5.6 patch 후 contrast 재확인** (font-size 13→15px / padding 2px 7px → 2px 8px / line-height 1.4 신규): 15px kbd `#0A0A0A` on `#FAFAFA` = **18.97:1** ✅ (font-size 증가에도 색상 무변 → ratio 동일), `.kbd-label` `#525252` on `#FFFFFF` = **7.81:1** ✅. Lighthouse + owner VoiceOver smoke 잔여 (Codex Q6 follow-up — task #14) |
